      <p>We cannot display the result of your DBS check online.</p>

      <h3 class="govuk-heading-m">Contact DBS</h3>
      <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
        <li>DBS Helpline: 03000 200 190 (Select option 2 and then press 1)</li>
        <li>Welsh language: 03000 200 191</li>
        <li>Relay UK: If you have difficulty with your speech or hearing, dial 18001 tjem 03000 200 192</li>
        <li>SignLive: If you are a British Sign Language (BSL) user, you can
